.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-DISABLE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-disable \- effectively disable a channel via extreme fees
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-disable
.I channel_id
.SH DESCRIPTION
Sets very high fees on the specified channel to deter routing, effectively
disabling it without closing it.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"status":"disabled_via_high_fees","channel_id":"<id>"}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-close-mutual (1),
.BR lightning-channel-fee-set-all (1)
